sequenceDiagram
    participant SGC as SharedGameCatalog
    participant Events
    participant Handler as NotificationHandler
    participant Domain as Notification
    participant DB as Database
    participant Cache as Redis
    participant Email as SMTP Service

    Note over SGC: User's share request approved

    SGC->>Events: Publish ShareRequestApprovedEvent
    Note right of SGC: {requestId, userId, sharedGameId}

    Events->>Handler: Handle(ShareRequestApprovedEvent)

    Handler->>Handler: Determine notification type
    Handler->>Handler: Build notification content

    Handler->>Domain: Notification.Create(userId, type, title, message, link)
    Domain->>Domain: Type = ShareRequestApproved
    Domain->>Domain: Severity = Success
    Domain->>Domain: IsRead = false
    Domain->>Domain: CreatedAt = UtcNow

    Handler->>DB: SaveAsync(notification)
    DB-->>Handler: Notification saved ✓

    Handler->>Cache: InvalidateKey("unread-count:{userId}")
    Cache-->>Handler: Cache invalidated ✓

    Handler->>Handler: Check if email required
    Note over Handler: ShareRequestApproved requires email

    Handler->>Email: SendEmailAsync(to, subject, body)
    Email->>Email: Connect to SMTP
    Email->>Email: Send email with notification content
    Email-->>Handler: Email sent ✓

    Handler-->>Events: Notification created ✓

    Note over Domain: User sees notification in app
    Note over Email: User receives email alert
